Dz0kElUt1cfxT71ww">Thanh Hư động ký - 清虛洞記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-T%C6%B0-Di%E1%BB%85n/Th%E1%BA%BF-t%E1%BB%AD-y%E1%BA%BFn-t%E1%BB%8Bch-t%E1%BB%91-thi/poem-7gzqvJRzEcK9hgXtxFdLew">Thế tử yến tịch tố thi - 世子燕席索詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-T%C6%B0-Di%E1%BB%85n/author-yjRlicU3gV4B06v3YivzTw">Lý Tư Diễn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%C3%ADnh-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%E1%BB%8B-ca/poem-_LCWpePDXkg4EpU_D5o3fg">Thính Dương thị ca - 聽楊氏歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tu%C3%BD-vi-m%C3%A3-tru%E1%BB%B5-ch%C6%B0-c%C3%B4ng-hu%E1%BB%81-t%E1%BB%ADu-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-khan/poem-SNR5C4s-13yOCWQM6nJBxQ">Tuý vi mã truỵ, chư công huề tửu tương khan - 醉為馬墜，諸公攜酒相看</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
